                q += 1 #increment q and compare with next larger value 
            else: #if larger than stop comparing values with next larger value 
                r -= 1 #decrement r and compare with next smaller value 
                if q == r: break #if it's equal break out of while loop and return a sorted list (sorted on left side) 
        self._swap(p, q) #swap back the largest element in the left side of the list with its correct position in the right side of the list (at position q) 
```

